Token.Abstract: The BXUAttachmentImageViewDelegate protocol defines the methods a delegate of a BXUAttachmentImageView object should implement. The methods of this protocol notify the delegate when the imageview has been tapped.
Notifies the delegate that the imageView has been tapped by the user for a message with an image attached.

Parameter.Name: attachmentImageView
Parameter.Abstract: The BXUAttachmentImageView object tapped by the user.

Parameter.Name: message
Parameter.Abstract: the message associated with the imageView.
